data.description: $10,000 Incentive for buyers to lower interest rate "Beautiful one-story home In North Park subdivision without neighbor association. Fresh paint inside and exterior recently added laminated flooring so "No carpet at all" Check out all the just replaced light fixtures-The desired location makes it even better 17 miles from Downtown Austin- 3 miles from the Domain Outdoor Mall offering a variety of upscale shops & department stores plus dining options & a cinema. did I mention The Q2 Soccer Stadium is just within walking distance?   Cozy home with plenty of windows for outside views and lighting. A fireplace That Will Make You Want To Stay Inside All Winter---The backyard is completely fenced for privacy a place where you can get out and enjoy the out-of-doors with your family and friends. enjoy cookouts and entertaining, Plenty of space for a pool and outdoor kitchen for your summer days
